
# https://ddewaele.github.io/running-jekyll-in-docker/

docker run --rm --volume="$PWD:/srv/jekyll" --volume="$PWD/vendor/bundle:/usr/local/bundle" -it jekyll/jekyll:3.8 jekyll build

docker run --rm --name myblog --volume="$PWD:/srv/jekyll" --volume="$PWD/vendor/bundle:/usr/local/bundle" -p 4000:4000 -it jekyll/jekyll:3.8 jekyll serve --watch --drafts



https://mmistakes.github.io/minimal-mistakes/docs/docs-2-2/#installation




https://jekyllrb.com/docs/configuration/options/